      <title>[인사] 대법원</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2026/02/07/QFX467X5KFCZJB34ERVPXHCR3I/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/obituary-personnel/2026/02/07/QFX467X5KFCZJB34ERVPXHCR3I/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
